    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>翻译是使用在线翻译器完成的。</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/95debb7fe26ad95ad10350c539cdebf6.avif?t=1751099947\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习如何与不同的方块（磁铁、门户等）互动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/38e0b5c5f2770eca1d3ad3f71dc6b845.poster.avif?t=1751099947\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/38e0b5c5f2770eca1d3ad3f71dc6b845.webm?t=1751099947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/38e0b5c5f2770eca1d3ad3f71dc6b845.mp4?t=1751099947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/25e781f4312c1ebd6babd518eb17373b.poster.avif?t=1751099947\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/25e781f4312c1ebd6babd518eb17373b.webm?t=1751099947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/25e781f4312c1ebd6babd518eb17373b.mp4?t=1751099947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/405f08ce418cf9d301e661d98f817ac1.avif?t=1751099947\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决 60 多个手工制作的关卡，其中许多关卡有多种解决方案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/8f54a86c0fbedd7530b6a630edd44cb2.poster.avif?t=1751099947\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/8f54a86c0fbedd7530b6a630edd44cb2.webm?t=1751099947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/8f54a86c0fbedd7530b6a630edd44cb2.mp4?t=1751099947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/66dd1998d4cebf37e1d27552b855ddaf.avif?t=1751099947\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用命令（步进、跳跃等）来操纵 C.U.B.E. 的位置和方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/9a3cd51060bc9a91a349c5f28b88c125.poster.avif?t=1751099947\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/9a3cd51060bc9a91a349c5f28b88c125.webm?t=1751099947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223840/extras/9a3cd51060bc9a91a349c5f28b88c125.mp4?t=1751099947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速指南</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有测试均由区块组成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要通过测试，请将 C.U.B.E. 移至终点。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要特别注意块组件以及用户界面细节。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果有什么不清楚的话，请使用数据库，也许它会有所帮助。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
